messages.content: 你好！很高兴为你提供决策支持。无论是生活中的小选择，还是重要的人生规划，我都可以帮你理清思路、分析利弊。请告诉我你目前需要帮助的具体问题或决策场景，我们可以一步步探讨！

Of course! I'm here to help you think through decisions in a clear and structured way. Whether you're facing a personal, professional, or any other kind of choice, I can assist by breaking down options, weighing pros and cons, and asking questions to clarify your goals.

What decision are you currently working on? Let’s start there!
